         "text": [
            {
               "text": "### Imagens de Ashmolean\n\nEstas imagens são protegidas por direitos autorais de Ashmolean e permitidas para uso de acordo com a licença determinada por eles.\n\nPara visualizar todas as imagens, use as setas esquerda e direita no slide abaixo.",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "markdown",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<p><div class=\"htSlides\"><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">1 / 4</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgEA\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgEA', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Trecho do épico de <i>Enmerkar e o Lord de Aratta</i>. © Ashmolean Museum, University of Oxford (<htcite0>).</div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">2 / 4</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgHarappaW\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgHarappaW', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Selo de Harappa. © Ashmolean Museum, University of Oxford (<htcite1>). Compartilhado sob a licença <a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc/4.0/\" target=\"_blank\">Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial-ShareAlike 4.0 International (CC BY-NC-SA 4.0).</div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">3 / 4</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgS\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgS', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Estatuetas da sexta dinastia. © Ashmolean Museum, University of Oxford (<htcite2>).</div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">4 / 4</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgKL\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgKL', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Lista dos Reis Sumérios. © Ashmolean Museum, University of Oxford (<htcite3>).</div></div><i class=\"fa-solid fa-chevron-left htSlidePrev\" onclick=\"htPlusDivs(-1);\"></i><i class=\"fa-solid fa-chevron-right htSlideNext\" onclick=\"htPlusDivs(1);\"></i></div></p>",
